text: Joseph Grech (born 26 March 1935) is a Maltese former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960, 1968 and 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Maltese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Malta Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1972 Summer Olympics
